reviewText: My absolute favorite Southern Gospel group: They don't just sing it from their heads, but also from their hearts, and they believe everything they're singing, plus, they also know how to have fun! I watch it alot!

Love watching this DVD. Like Gone with Doug Anderson. Little is Much and Oh What a Saviour with Ernie Haase are my favorites. Suppertime with George Younce is awesome. I enjoyed everything about this DVD, however!
